quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,127,"IbĂŽahim akked IsmaĂąil, mi ssalayen leĂȘyuv n Uxxam: ""a Mass nne$! Eqbel s$uĂŽne$, KeĂ§Ă§, s tidep, d Win Isellen, d Amusnaw."
  2,128,"A Mass nne$! Err ane$ d imvuĂąen iK, u, si dderya nne$, lois ar aK ianzen. Mel a$ isekkiren nne$, Ssuref a$. KeĂ§Ă§, s tidep, Tessurufev, TepĂȘunuv."
  2,129,"A Mass nne$! Azen asen d amazan segsen, ad asen iqqaĂŽ issekniyen iK, ad asen isseĂȘfev Tazmamt akked Ă»Ă»wab, a ten izzizdeg. KeĂ§Ă§, s tidep, d Uzmir, d Bab n Ă»Ă»wab""."
  2,130,"Anwa iugin ddin n IbĂŽahim, siwa win iccemten iman is? Ni$ Nefren it di ddunit. Di laxeĂŽt, neppa, war ccekk, seg iĂąaĂŽviyen."
  2,131,"Mi s Inna Mass is: ""anez""! Inna: ""unze$ aS i Mass imavalen""."
  2,132,"IweĂ»Ă»a yis IbĂŽahim arraw is - akken IaĂąqub -: ""a yarraw iw, Ăebbi, s tidep, Ifren awen ddin, ur ppemmtet siwa ma tunzem""."
  2,133,"Ne$ tellam d inagan mi d ters tmeppant ar YaĂąqub, mi inna i tarwa s: ""anwa ara tĂąabdem deffir i""? Nnan: ""a naĂąbed Ăebbi k, u Ăebbi n lejdud ik: IbĂŽahim, IsmaĂąil, IsĂȘaq. Ăebbi Yiwen. Nekwni nunez aS""."
  2,134,"Wigi d lois i iĂąaddan. Ines ayen ikseb, nnwen ayen tkesbem. Ur kwen steqsayen $ef wayen xeddmen."
